fields.content:
I was pleased to receive #Armenia’s Ambassador, H.E. @sahak_sargsyan, for a courtesy call. We had fruitful discussions on Burundi’s Chairmanship of the @_AfricanUnion & on #Armenia–#Burundi bilateral relations, established for more than three decades. 
@armembeth
#Burundi4Africa

I had a fruitful exchange with H.E. Dr. @simoneknapp, Ambassador of #Austria to Ethiopia & the AU, on multilateral cooperation, including discussions on the @_AfricanUnion Chairmanship in 2026.
#Burundi4Africa
 @AustriainET

#Burundi’s Ambassador in Addis Ababa @willynyamitwe received in audience his counterpart of #Austria, Amb. @simoneknapp. Fruitful exchanges on multilateral cooperation, including the @_AfricanUnion Chairmanship in 2026.
#Burundi4Africa
@AustriainET

